reviewText: Is not complete! So sad , because I thought , I' m going to watch the all serie. But is not complete. SO SAD.  Please all people who read this  comment. Don't buy this movie.. I hope the customers listen to me  so you don't waist your money.
If that the case that it's not the complete series,  then I won't buy it. How sad and disappointed  , because it is truly an excellent series. There's got to be another way to get it.

Film was good quality, but is not the complete series. I was very unhappy because it's only clips from the story. Does not even tell you the entire story. Example: The woman that is always causing problems only come out two times, once she is listening ( Listen to what and what was the point???) and the other one she tells moses the story of his past. I would love to return it because it was just like seen nothing but clips from different parts of the movie. The entire story is just little pcs and I seen the entire series. It would have been nice if they atleast give you a story but is nothing but different parts that don't make sense... I was very unhappy and I didn't like it at all. A lot of the actors didn't come out. Looks more like previews. short movie, not even long enough for a movie. I thought it was the origional series.. well if it was a movie, I would have been satisfy if at least had a story.
